sources.description: This version has improved contrast and brightness. “Comedy-drama with some good moments” “Likable” “Lively and fun” “Slight but fun” (IMDB reviews quotes). Pre-code comedy, romance and crime drama staring Eddie Quillan and Robert Armstrong. Ginger Rogers appears in a major supporting role. Adequate production values. Surprisingly engaging. IMDB rating 5.8. Directed by Albert Rogell; Released in 1931. Complete print. AKA “Eddie Cuts In”
